      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "NGINX会带上FinTech_AuthVault的头部往下传，但真正的认证验证是Workhorse去Gitaly做的。Gitaly会回一个Auth Verify，然后Workhorse再告诉Puma Auth Confirm，Puma确认OK后整个链路才继续。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "Workhorse",
        "Gitaly",
        "Puma",
