      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主链路：Git Client异步调用LoadBalancer，同步到NGINX，再到Workhorse、Puma，Puma返回200后Workhorse去调Gitaly。认证部分我画成Workhorse和Gitaly之间的双向确认，然后Workhorse回传Puma。",
      "elements_involved": [
